notes.body: Hello ​Anjan,     Greetings from PharmEasy!  ​   Please be informed, we are unable to comply with your request and erase the data. We have to produce/show any or all transactions or interactions, past or present when asked for by relevant Governmental authorities.    However, please confirm if you wish to deactivate your account.     Let me inform you that, once the account is deactivated then we cannot process any request or reactivate the account. Once confirmed our team will reach out to complete the account deactivation process on a registered mobile number to confirm if you requested account deactivation. If yes, OTP will be generated and will be sent to your registered mobile number. Once the OTP will be shared by you to the team then will go ahead and block the customer's account.   ​   With regards to the promotional notifications, we always try to keep our customers updated on our offers. However, we apologize for the inconvenience caused due to our promotional messages.  ​   Regarding the promotional calls, I have highlighted the issue to the Operations team. We will respond with the update as soon as we receive any from them.   Please be assured, I have forwarded your request to unsubscribe your number '9029030982' from getting the promotional notifications. It will take 3 working days to process it completely. You will only receive your order-related information.   Further, if you wish to unsubscribe from getting the promotional notifications on your email id too, I request you to open your latest promotional email and hit unsubscribe at the bottom right-hand side corner to stop email promotions.   I certainly hope this helps and appreciate your understanding and patience in the meanwhile.  ​   ​Awaiting your response.     Regards,  Manisha

With regards to the promotional notifications, we always try to keep our customers updated on our offers. However, we apologize for the inconvenience caused due to our promotional messages.

Regarding the promotional calls, I have highlighted the issue to the Operations team. We will respond with the update as soon as we receive any from them.

Further, if you wish to unsubscribe from getting the promotional notifications on your email id too, I request you to open your latest promotional email and hit unsubscribe at the bottom right-hand side corner to stop email promotions.

I certainly hope this helps and appreciate your understanding and patience in the meanwhile.
​
​Awaiting your response.

Regards,
Manisha

notes.body_html:
Hello Ajeet Kumar,

Greetings from team PharmEasy!
 
We are sorry to inform you that your order #654506505422225408-32212 was canceled on 08th December 2025 because the area selected in your order is currently unserviceable. We can understand how upsetting this must be for you. We are sorry for the inconvenience caused to you.

We tried to called you however we are unable to establish contact with you.
 
Please be informed, your pin code is serviceable, however, your area location is out of our serviceable area. You may place a new order with an alternate address and we will process it accordingly. 
 
The cancellation refund of Rs.1241.41 /- has been initiated on 8th December 2025 and the same will be credited to your source account within 5-7 business days.We appreciate your patience and understanding in this regard.
 
We are marking the ticket as resolved. If you have any queries, please feel free to get back to us.
 
For any further assistance, please reopen this ticket or reach out to us through our support channels, in the App or website, listed in the 'Need Help' section.
 
Thank you for choosing PharmEasy. Have a great day ahead!
 
Regards,
PharmEasy
